Doc
  https://github.com/airbnb/enzyme/
React install
  npm install chai enzyme mocha
  npm uninstall enzyme
  npm install enzyme@3.3.0

  Chai is an assertion library
    assert, expect or should
  Enzyme makes it easier to
    assert, manipulate, and traverse your React Components
  Mocha is test framework running

test single file:
  yarn test app/assets/javascripts/apps/tests/marketplace/search/details/DefaultDetails.spec.jsx
  node_modules/.bin/jest app/assets/javascripts/apps/tests/marketplace/search/details/DefaultDetails.spec.jsx  
  node_modules/.bin/mocha mocha.test.js
  
Test all files:
  yarn test
  yarn dev
  yarn test
  yarn test_watch

